title: Abandoned Tomb of Dinna
story: For a long time the tomb of Dinna was considered lost. Recently a pack of albino snakes have made its lair here. The tomb of Dinna is a place of growth of a highly valued specie of flowers.

notes.text: A reinforced crate containing rations and a long sword.
Gems among rubble on the ground.
A massive wooden door on the western wall.
A wooden altar, puts a person to sleep when the candles on it are lit.
A rear entrance into the tomb.
